The paper proposes a method for multi-disease diagnosis using medical knowledge based on first-order logic and recursive neural network. This involves the representation of knowledge using high-dimensional and continuous vectors, which is a common approach in artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with natural language processing (NLP) and semantic information, which are relevant to cs.CL. Additionally, the use of electronic medical records (EMRs) involves data management and retrieval, which are relevant to cs.DB and cs.IR.
